-- Infrastructure fund Ancala names new partner
-- 
-- Sun Apr 13, 2014 05:00PM EDT
-- None



LONDON, April 13 (Reuters) - Independent UK-based infrastructure investment fund Ancala Partners said on Sunday that Vincent Gerritsen, a senior investment manager at Dutch pension fund PGGM, would join as partner from June 1.

Gerritsen joins a team of 10 focusing on investments in the UK and Europe, Ancala said in a statement.